Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.54,0:00:02.48,Base,,0,0,0,,Go away.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.67,0:00:04.90,Base,,0,0,0,,Don't come closer!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.34,0:00:07.34,Base,,0,0,0,,Ai!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.43,0:00:20.29,Base,,0,0,0,,No, that's not it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.89,0:00:23.26,Base,,0,0,0,,I just wanted
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.44,0:00:25.26,Base,,0,0,0,,to apologize to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.24,0:00:53.49,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur9}Everyone dreams of becoming a superstar at least once
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.49,0:00:58.77,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur9}So that you can make the world envious
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.77,0:01:01.52,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur9}1, 2, 3, quick like Allegro
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.52,0:01:03.79,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur9}Hold that hand and come
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.79,0:01:08.34,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur9}Let's build a rainbow together at Andante
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.53,0:01:14.60,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur9}You aren't anyone right now
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.60,0:01:19.71,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur9}So any of your future can come true
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.71,0:01:25.72,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur9}Your dream is just beginning
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.21,0:01:30.39,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur9}Little by little, you can become yourself
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.39,0:01:36.31,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur9}Tomorrow's gonna blow another wind
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.31,0:01:40.23,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur9}So dream as many times as you want
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.23,0:01:45.71,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur9}Someday, become the stage's sparkling star
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.71,0:01:50.92,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur9}so that the spotlight shines upon you
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.78,0:02:04.50,Base,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"Tears Overwritten"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.33,0:02:06.49,Base,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What do I do?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.58,0:02:10.82,Base,,0,0,0,,I'm a horrible person.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.30,0:02:14.64,Base,,0,0,0,,I left Watanabe with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.55,0:02:20.87,Base,,0,0,0,,It's my fault Naracchi was forced to quit JPX.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.89,0:02:23.38,Base,,0,0,0,,What do you mean by that?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.52,0:02:31.15,Base,,0,0,0,,I'm not Ai, but if you want, I can hear you out.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.15,0:02:32.86,Base,,0,0,0,,I mean, I {\i1}am {\i0}her room-
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.86,0:02:35.07,Base,,0,0,0,,Alright! No sharing personal information!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.07,0:02:37.68,Base,,0,0,0,,Mr. Narata?! What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.24,0:02:42.58,Base,,0,0,0,,I wasn't going to let the two of you go by yourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.58,0:02:44.90,Base,,0,0,0,,Who knew if this guy was a total perv.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.00,0:02:46.96,Base,,0,0,0,,A... total perv?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.96,0:02:50.13,Base,,0,0,0,,He's not a perv, he's a stalker!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.13,0:02:51.34,Base,,0,0,0,,U-Um.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.04,0:02:55.57,Base,,0,0,0,,Perv, stalker, call me whatever you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.57,0:02:57.26,Base,,0,0,0,,It's my fault, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.26,0:02:58.88,Base,,0,0,0,,Sorry to bother you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.88,0:02:59.95,Base,,0,0,0,,Please, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.60,0:03:05.77,Base,,0,0,0,,Ai might've told me that we weren't friends,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.77,0:03:12.42,Base,,0,0,0,,but even though it sucks, \NI still want to try to be friends with her!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.77,0:03:16.78,Base,,0,0,0,,Could you please tell me what happened\Nbetween you two, Mister Stalker?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.58,0:03:30.65,Base,,0,0,0,,Watanabe Sarasa's with a guy? No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.83,0:03:33.61,Base,,0,0,0,,He's super lame, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.17,0:03:35.83,Base,,0,0,0,,It suits her in a way.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.13,0:03:38.92,Base - Top,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.92,0:03:39.88,Base - Top,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.88,0:03:42.33,Base,,0,0,0,,What, Mr. Narata's there, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.88,0:03:42.33,Base - Top,,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.06,0:03:49.52,Base,,0,0,0,,Um,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.52,0:03:53.15,Base,,0,0,0,,I used to be an unemployed shut-in\Nwho never left the house.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.15,0:03:54.57,Base,,0,0,0,,Wow, Mister Shut-In!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.23,0:04:00.31,Base,,0,0,0,,I was never good with people,\Nso I started ditching school.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.74,0:04:04.81,Base,,0,0,0,,I spent every day watching anime,\Nplaying games, and browsing the internet.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.99,0:04:08.50,Base,,0,0,0,,I love anime, too!\NI'm super into {\i1}Floor Kings {\i0}right no-
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.50,0:04:11.00,Base,,0,0,0,,C'mon, let him talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.00,0:04:11.94,Base,,0,0,0,,Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.04,0:04:14.15,Base,,0,0,0,,One day,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.32,0:04:17.59,Base,,0,0,0,,I somehow had this music show on.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.51,0:04:21.66,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What? Who is this girl?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.97,0:04:25.01,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And why does she never try to smile?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.10,0:04:27.68,Base,,0,0,0,,It shocked me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.68,0:04:31.31,Base,,0,0,0,,She was not scared, or withered.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.31,0:04:34.19,Base,,0,0,0,,She reminded me of a fantasy princess,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.19,0:04:37.02,Base,,0,0,0,,or an ice queen who rules over the winter itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.02,0:04:39.66,Base,,0,0,0,,But then, there was that unforgettable day.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.18,0:04:45.41,Base,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"Local Mascot Meet n' Greet"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.18,0:04:45.41,Flashback,,0,0,0,,Today, we've brought a bunch of your\Nfavorite local mascots to meet the JPX48!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.37,0:04:48.62,Flashback,,0,0,0,,Which is your favorite, Komomo?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.62,0:04:52.19,Flashback,,0,0,0,,Oh, wow, I think I like Starry Boy the best!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.87,0:04:56.95,Base,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I knew 100% she'd fallen from heaven!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.50,0:05:01.79,Base,,0,0,0,,That day, June 23rd, the Naracchi Nation\Nopened to one and all!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.92,0:05:02.55,Base,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"ANONYMOUS: WELCOME TO\NTHE NARACCHI NATION"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.55,0:05:04.18,Base,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"ANONYMOUS: She's kinda cute"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.55,0:05:04.18,Base,,0,0,0,,Like when Commodore Perry came to Japan!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.22,0:05:08.72,Flashback,,0,0,0,,Even I want to...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.72,0:05:10.81,Flashback,,0,0,0,,I want to...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.81,0:05:12.38,Flashback,,0,0,0,,I want to open my borders, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.11,0:05:20.11,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I don't need to worry about how others see me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.11,0:05:22.10,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can just be myself.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.82,0:05:26.38,Flashback,,0,0,0,,A fellow Naracchi stan?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.83,0:05:31.85,Base,,0,0,0,,I made friends and started a part-time job.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.19,0:05:35.19,Base,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"JPX48 Handshake Event"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.50,0:05:35.87,Flashback,,0,0,0,,Please double-checking the number \Non your ticket before lining up!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.19,0:05:37.88,Base,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"Ai Narata"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.87,0:05:39.34,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\i1}How shall I express myself in such a limited time?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.34,0:05:43.13,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Will I be able to convey my millions of feelings?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.05,0:05:50.10,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I have to thank you. I have to!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.10,0:05:51.52,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I have to tell you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.52,0:05:59.38,Flashback,,0,0,0,,I-I...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.61,0:06:01.34,Flashback,,0,0,0,,Naracchi, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.78,0:06:02.70,Flashback,,0,0,0,,I love you so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.70,0:06:03.34,Flashback,,0,0,0,,Hey, sir-
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.69,0:06:05.81,Flashback,,0,0,0,,Let go, creep.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.82,0:06:10.70,Base,,0,0,0,,It took so long to crawl my way up,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.70,0:06:12.90,Base,,0,0,0,,but only a second to fall back into the abyss.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.87,0:06:15.40,Base,,0,0,0,,That's when I remembered.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.65,0:06:18.67,Base,,0,0,0,,"Yeah, I'm just a gross nerd."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.67,0:06:21.67,Base,,0,0,0,,It's not your fault at all, Mister Gross Nerd!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.67,0:06:24.88,Base,,0,0,0,,You poor guy! Cheer up, Mister Gross Otaku!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.88,0:06:27.47,Base,,0,0,0,,N-No, you don't need to worry about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.47,0:06:31.37,Base,,0,0,0,,But to make up for it,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.37,0:06:34.17,Base,,0,0,0,,Naracchi was forced to graduate without any ceremony.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.14,0:06:34.17,Base,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"RIP Naracchi lmao"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.14,0:06:34.17,Base,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"does she hate her fans??" "GJ Naracchi."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.23,0:06:39.98,Base,,0,0,0,,It was my fault for holding onto\NNaracchi's hand for too long.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.42,0:06:41.40,Base,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"Ai Narata EXPELLED from JPX"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.98,0:06:41.40,Base,,0,0,0,,But I was just one guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.40,0:06:45.18,Base,,0,0,0,,There wasn't anything I could do about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.61,0:06:48.20,Base,,0,0,0,,I knew it might've been selfish of me,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.20,0:06:50.68,Base,,0,0,0,,but I wanted to at least apologize to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.03,0:06:55.63,Base,,0,0,0,,But that probably just makes me\Neven more of a creep to Naracchi, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.54,0:06:59.59,Base,,0,0,0,,You don't seem like a bad person.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.59,0:07:00.44,Base,,0,0,0,,What's your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.54,0:07:01.79,Base,,0,0,0,,Mister Creepy Nerd.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.79,0:07:03.63,Base,,0,0,0,,Okay, Creepy Nerd.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.63,0:07:06.88,Base,,0,0,0,,Uh, sure, just call me that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.88,0:07:10.41,Base,,0,0,0,,So I've got good news and bad news.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.68,0:07:15.27,Base,,0,0,0,,The good news is that Ai\Ndoesn't hate you specifically.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.27,0:07:18.59,Base,,0,0,0,,She hates every man in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.59,0:07:19.29,Base,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.81,0:07:22.02,Base,,0,0,0,,She'd been holding back for the whole handshaking event.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.02,0:07:25.15,Base,,0,0,0,,And she just happened to break when it was your turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.03,0:07:28.28,Base,,0,0,0,,Now for the bad news:
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.28,0:07:32.81,Base,,0,0,0,,Ai isn't as attached to JPX as you hope.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.33,0:07:37.29,Base,,0,0,0,,Unfortunately, I can probably say the\Nsame thing about the Kouka Troupe.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.16,0:07:39.04,Base,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"Tear Spray"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.16,0:07:43.13,Base,,0,0,0,,At some point, Ai gave up on the world
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.13,0:07:46.55,Base,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0, 1000)}and started hiding her emotions.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.30,0:07:52.43,Base,,0,0,0,,Right now, she's just trying to find a\Nplace where she can relax and feel safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.97,0:07:58.54,Flashback,,0,0,0,,Dealing with people is annoying\Nand a waste of my time.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.35,0:08:01.02,Base,,0,0,0,,It's such a waste.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.77,0:08:04.92,Base,,0,0,0,,I mean, the first time I saw Ai,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.36,0:08:08.19,Base,,0,0,0,,I thought she looked like Alice stumbling into Wonderland.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.24,0:08:11.45,Base,,0,0,0,,"How perfect for Kouka," I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.45,0:08:15.31,Base,,0,0,0,,"She would be the type of person to stand\N and shine in the center of the Kouka stage."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.04,0:08:23.27,Base,,0,0,0,,I knew I wanted to stand up on that stage with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.46,0:08:26.47,Base,,0,0,0,,Narata, where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.47,0:08:28.20,Base,,0,0,0,,It's almost time for dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.63,0:08:31.41,Base,,0,0,0,,Watanabe's not back yet.\NI'm going to go look for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.80,0:08:34.68,Base,,0,0,0,,I saw her alone with a guy earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.68,0:08:35.21,Base,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.13,0:08:37.17,Base,,0,0,0,,Excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.13,0:08:42.20,Base,,0,0,0,,What a great pic.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.31,0:08:46.05,Base,,0,0,0,,Now, what should I do with it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.78,0:08:52.93,Base,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She's not here. What do I do?.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.53,0:08:55.42,Base,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What if he did something to her?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.54,0:09:04.15,Base,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.22,0:09:14.38,Base,,0,0,0,,You're not half bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.38,0:09:16.29,Base,,0,0,0,,I am a rising Kouka star, after all!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.55,0:09:19.29,Base,,0,0,0,,Well then, can you do {\i1}this{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.06,0:09:21.83,Base,,0,0,0,,Matrix!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.40,0:09:29.32,Base,,0,0,0,,Like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.57,0:09:34.86,Base,,0,0,0,,Ai!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.86,0:09:37.89,Base,,0,0,0,,You came back. What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.33,0:09:40.45,Base,,0,0,0,,What the hell?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.45,0:09:41.45,Base,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.37,0:09:45.12,Base,,0,0,0,,I really
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.12,0:09:46.42,Base,,0,0,0,,hate you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.59,0:09:51.21,Base,,0,0,0,,You... hate me?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.85,0:10:07.48,Base,,0,0,0,,Well, this is unusual. \NI can barely hear you, Watanabe.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.48,0:10:09.94,Base,,0,0,0,,Usually you're far too loud than necessary.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.94,0:10:11.11,Base,,0,0,0,,Sorry, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.11,0:10:13.36,Base,,0,0,0,,And Yamada, you too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.36,0:10:15.07,Base,,0,0,0,,S-Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.07,0:10:18.64,Base,,0,0,0,,I'm on a diet right now, so I don't have the energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.82,0:10:22.65,Base,,0,0,0,,Oh? Well, diet's fine, but take care of yourself, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.74,0:10:23.62,Base,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.62,0:10:25.79,Base,,0,0,0,,Okay, let's split into quartets!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.79,0:10:29.00,Base,,0,0,0,,Yamada, Hoshino, Narata, and Watanabe!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.76,0:10:36.83,Base,,0,0,0,,Hey, Ai?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.26,0:10:41.00,Base,,0,0,0,,I don't know why you got so mad at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.43,0:10:43.56,Base,,0,0,0,,Could you tell me why?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.52,0:10:51.56,Base,,0,0,0,,Uh... Ai?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.40,0:10:55.72,Base,,0,0,0,,If I tell you, will you finally leave me alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.82,0:10:56.42,Base,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.57,0:11:02.01,Base,,0,0,0,,I felt horrible for running off\Nand leaving you there with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.08,0:11:07.12,Base,,0,0,0,,It took me everything to go back.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.12,0:11:08.91,Base,,0,0,0,,And yet, it was so foolish.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.58,0:11:10.61,Base,,0,0,0,,What was foolish?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.17,0:11:16.45,Base,,0,0,0,,You guys were dancing and \Nseemed like having fun, {\i1}that{\i0} was foolish!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.05,0:11:18.14,Base,,0,0,0,,Ai...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.18,0:11:20.66,Base,,0,0,0,,That doesn't make sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.89,0:11:21.72,Base,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.72,0:11:26.69,Base,,0,0,0,,If you came back because you were worried\Nabout me, then you should've been happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.31,0:11:32.92,Base,,0,0,0,,If you were worried, you should've\Nbeen glad to see I was okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.36,0:11:36.15,Base,,0,0,0,,You're just trying to pick a fight now!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.15,0:11:38.18,Base,,0,0,0,,Just don't bother me anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.28,0:11:41.56,Base,,0,0,0,,Fine, then! We're {\i1}through{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.91,0:11:43.27,Base,,0,0,0,,Nothing's through!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.66,0:11:45.71,Base,,0,0,0,,I told you, we {\i1}aren't friends{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.97,0:12:10.10,Base,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I told a someone I wanted to be\Nfriends with that "we're through."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.10,0:12:11.59,Base,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"We're through"?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.98,0:12:16.40,Base,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But I still can't bring myself to hate her.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.40,0:12:21.28,Base,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She has so many qualities that I don't.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.28,0:12:24.07,Base,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can't help but admire her.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.87,0:12:33.46,Base,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You don't need to rush since\N you're just getting to know each other.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.46,0:12:35.80,Base,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Just take your time and keep at it.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.55,0:12:40.76,Base,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But you might not get what you want.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.76,0:12:45.45,Base,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Your feelings could just be one-sided forever, \Nwhich you can only watch over.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.80,0:12:49.10,Base,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But I think that's beautiful in its own way.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.10,0:12:51.27,Base,,0,0,0,,{\i1}One-sided feelings forever, huh?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.31,0:12:54.57,Base,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Akiya is so poetic sometimes.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.48,0:13:00.69,Base,,0,0,0,,Dammit, Kouzaburou! \NStop tweeting and pretending to be me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.69,0:13:03.85,Base,,0,0,0,,I figured it would be too heavy\Nfor you to handle, Akiya.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.29,0:13:13.79,Base,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Let her be late.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.97,0:13:24.34,Base,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I don't want to go to class.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.84,0:13:27.04,Base,,0,0,0,,Watanabe!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.35,0:13:28.72,Base,,0,0,0,,Yes, Mr. Narata.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.72,0:13:32.25,Base,,0,0,0,,I can't find Ai. Have you seen her?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.43,0:13:36.90,Base,,0,0,0,,Oh, I thought she felt bad and went back to the dorm.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.90,0:13:38.51,Base,,0,0,0,,Is she skipping class?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.65,0:13:40.57,Base,,0,0,0,,I hope that's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.57,0:13:42.32,Base,,0,0,0,,It doesn't look like she went back to the dorm,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.32,0:13:43.72,Base,,0,0,0,,and she's not picking up her phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.28,0:13:48.62,Base,,0,0,0,,Ai's not the type to wander around town,\N because of how she sticks out.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.24,0:13:53.16,Base,,0,0,0,,And she wouldn't want to give strangers\Nany reason to talk to her,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.16,0:13:55.42,Base,,0,0,0,,so she's likely not breaking any rules.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.17,0:13:58.11,Base,,0,0,0,,Thanks. I'll keep looking for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.29,0:14:02.54,Base,,0,0,0,,Um, do you think she might've been feeling\Nhomesick and went back to Tokyo?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.42,0:14:05.66,Base,,0,0,0,,I really doubt that's the case.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.39,0:14:08.72,Base,,0,0,0,,Watanabe?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.72,0:14:10.72,Base,,0,0,0,,Could we borrow you for a moment?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.57,0:14:24.85,Base,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I wish Watanabe would drop out of school.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.45,0:14:29.24,Base,,0,0,0,,Whoa, hol' up, isn't that Naracchi from JPX?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.24,0:14:30.08,Base,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.08,0:14:31.45,Base,,0,0,0,,Yo, it totally is!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.45,0:14:33.23,Base,,0,0,0,,Holy shit, cute as hell!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.77,0:14:37.75,Base,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Where could Ai have gone?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.25,0:14:40.71,Base,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Did she run away because I said we were through?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.71,0:14:42.05,Base,,0,0,0,,{\i1}No way, she wouldn't.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.05,0:14:43.01,Base,,0,0,0,,Watanabe!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.01,0:14:44.07,Base,,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.13,0:14:45.38,Base,,0,0,0,,Are you listening?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.02,0:14:47.17,Base,,0,0,0,,This is you, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.66,0:14:50.89,Base,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"That's a Kouka student, right?"
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.93,0:14:50.89,Base,,0,0,0,,Whoa, that's me! It's totally me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.89,0:14:52.92,Base,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"I thought their school rules\Nwere stricter than this?"
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.89,0:14:52.92,Base,,0,0,0,,And they've blacked out my eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.02,0:14:55.60,Base,,0,0,0,,So you admit it, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.60,0:14:56.88,Base,,0,0,0,,That he's your boyfriend?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.88,0:14:57.34,Base,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.35,0:15:00.86,Base,,0,0,0,,The Kouka Troupe does allow romantic relationships,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.86,0:15:04.53,Base,,0,0,0,,but you can't be so open about it that\Nothers can get a picture of you two alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.53,0:15:06.20,Base,,0,0,0,,Especially when you're still a student.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.20,0:15:08.69,Base,,0,0,0,,Oh, but we weren't alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.69,0:15:10.37,Base,,0,0,0,,Mr. Narata was with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.37,0:15:13.39,Base,,0,0,0,,Really? I'll confirm it with him, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.49,0:15:19.00,Base,,0,0,0,,Oh, no. If this gets out, I'm sure a few\Nsecond-years will have it out for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.00,0:15:22.29,Base,,0,0,0,,But I guess your boyfriend is worth it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.32,0:15:25.59,Base,,0,0,0,,He's not my boyfriend, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.17,0:15:31.26,Base,,0,0,0,,Um, can we continue this later?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.26,0:15:32.72,Base,,0,0,0,,Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.72,0:15:35.02,Base,,0,0,0,,I just remembered something important I gotta do!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.02,0:15:36.25,Base,,0,0,0,,Don't you dare go!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.10,0:15:38.27,Base,,0,0,0,,It was you, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.27,0:15:38.84,Base,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.15,0:15:42.55,Base,,0,0,0,,You took it {\i1}way {\i0}too far this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.65,0:15:44.84,Base,,0,0,0,,I have no idea what you're talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.57,0:15:47.54,Base,,0,0,0,,Do you hate me or something, Risa?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.91,0:15:52.16,Base,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"Call from Sarasa Watanabe"
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.70,0:15:55.08,Base,,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.74,0:15:57.50,Base,,0,0,0,,Actually, I'm still in Kobe.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.62,0:15:59.73,Base,,0,0,0,,Naracchi?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.84,0:16:03.80,Base,,0,0,0,,I'm bored of the ocean.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.55,0:16:07.74,Base,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I've never skipped school before,\N so I don't know what to do next.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.51,0:16:14.25,Base,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I wonder if they noticed I'm gone,\Nor if they're even worried about me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.47,0:16:16.89,Base,,0,0,0,,Hey, 'scuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.00,0:16:19.06,Base,,0,0,0,,I'm kinda lost. Could you help?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.85,0:16:25.27,Base,,0,0,0,,Whoa, hol' up, are you Naracchi?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.27,0:16:27.73,Base,,0,0,0,,Yay, how 'bout a selfie?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.73,0:16:28.93,Base,,0,0,0,,Stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.11,0:16:30.89,Base,,0,0,0,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.11,0:16:33.12,Base,,0,0,0,,Let go, you creeps!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.12,0:16:34.41,Base - Top,,0,0,0,,Yo, what the hell?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.20,0:16:38.50,Base,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Why is it so hard for me to live in this world?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.41,0:16:36.61,Base - Top,,0,0,0,,He just wanted a selfie!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.04,0:16:42.75,Base,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Why do I have to be like this?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.75,0:16:45.42,Base,,0,0,0,,No. Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.42,0:16:46.75,Base,,0,0,0,,Please stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.75,0:16:48.36,Base,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.63,0:16:50.59,Base,,0,0,0,,Stop that, right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.26,0:16:55.96,Base,,0,0,0,,Get your dirty paws
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.01,0:17:01.36,Base,,0,0,0,,off of her!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.77,0:17:06.67,Base,,0,0,0,,What the heck?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.67,0:17:08.11,Base,,0,0,0,,She obviously doesn't like it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.11,0:17:09.89,Base,,0,0,0,,I'm telling you to let her go!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.11,0:17:10.87,Base,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.87,0:17:12.40,Base,,0,0,0,,I'm not scared!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.40,0:17:14.54,Base,,0,0,0,,I'm not scared of someone like you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.07,0:17:18.25,Base,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Oh, no... what do I do?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.95,0:17:21.11,Base,,0,0,0,,Whoa, she really was here!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.16,0:17:23.04,Base,,0,0,0,,Ai!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.04,0:17:23.69,Base,,0,0,0,,Ai!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.63,0:17:30.16,Base,,0,0,0,,I said we were through, Ai,\Nbut I'll help you just this once.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.63,0:17:32.67,Base,,0,0,0,,Just this once, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.60,0:17:41.50,Base,,0,0,0,,Help! These guys won't leave us alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.50,0:17:42.27,Base,,0,0,0,,She's so loud.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.27,0:17:44.02,Base,,0,0,0,,Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.02,0:17:45.06,Base,,0,0,0,,And she's huge.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.06,0:17:49.07,Base,,0,0,0,,These guys are harassing two sweet, innocent girls!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.90,0:17:51.24,Base,,0,0,0,,Shit, cops!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.24,0:17:53.66,Base,,0,0,0,,Fine, we'll let you off the hook this time!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.49,0:17:58.93,Base,,0,0,0,,Weaklings.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.21,0:18:06.12,Base,,0,0,0,,You shouldn't do that!\N You're coming to the station with us!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.12,0:18:07.94,Base,,0,0,0,,Wait, that's the wrong guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.50,0:18:12.84,Base,,0,0,0,,You're a teacher at Kouka?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.84,0:18:16.20,Base,,0,0,0,,Yes. My name is Narata Taichi.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.68,0:18:19.20,Base,,0,0,0,,How did you know I was here?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.39,0:18:22.43,Base,,0,0,0,,Mister Creepy Nerd figured it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.43,0:18:24.96,Base,,0,0,0,,I got his number before he left.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.23,0:18:28.31,Base,,0,0,0,,The ocean! She's gotta be near the ocean!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.31,0:18:29.15,Base,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.15,0:18:34.11,Base,,0,0,0,,March 2018 issue of POCO mag\Nand the JPX official newsletter,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.11,0:18:36.22,Base,,0,0,0,,she said the ocean makes her feel calm!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.57,0:18:40.06,Base,,0,0,0,,That doesn't really\Nnarrow it down, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.12,0:18:42.96,Base,,0,0,0,,I'll do a search on social media!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.79,0:18:47.96,Base,,0,0,0,,This is bad. I gotta find her...\NI gotta find her, fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.96,0:18:50.81,Base,,0,0,0,,And then he really {\i1}did {\i0}find you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.81,0:18:51.83,Base,,0,0,0,,Isn't that awesome?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.59,0:18:56.80,Base,,0,0,0,,Mister Creepy Nerd really\Ncares about you, Ai.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.64,0:19:01.35,Base,,0,0,0,,Watanabe, could you tell them your side of the story?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.35,0:19:02.29,Base,,0,0,0,,Sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.06,0:19:10.71,Base,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.24,0:19:19.40,Base,,0,0,0,,You've got blood. Wipe it with this.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.97,0:19:38.01,Base,,0,0,0,,I didn't mean to.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.94,0:19:40.13,Base,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.97,0:19:44.21,Base,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.81,0:19:51.21,Base,,0,0,0,,This is the best I can do right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.94,0:19:55.97,Base,,0,0,0,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.28,0:19:58.93,Base,,0,0,0,,Really, it's okay. Please don't cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.99,0:20:04.99,Base,,0,0,0,,I-- no, {\i1}we {\i0}only ever wanted
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.99,0:20:07.69,Base,,0,0,0,,to see you smile, Naracchi.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.46,0:20:12.13,Base,,0,0,0,,I don't think I'll ever get this close to you again,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.13,0:20:14.97,Base,,0,0,0,,so please let me keep your handkerchief.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.67,0:20:19.17,Base,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry for scaring you before.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.17,0:20:22.79,Base,,0,0,0,,One day, I'll come see you perform\Non the big Kouka stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.18,0:20:26.77,Base,,0,0,0,,When that day comes, \NI hope I'll see your beautiful smile once more.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.77,0:20:28.14,Base,,0,0,0,,Farewell.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.82,0:20:37.63,Base,,0,0,0,,And thank you. Until we meet again!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.54,0:20:50.37,Base,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"Hana no Michi: Flower Way"
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.87,0:20:50.27,Base,,0,0,0,,Mister Creepy Nerd was a pretty nice guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.37,0:20:54.79,Base,,0,0,0,,Oh, and his real name is Kitaouji Mikiya!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.79,0:20:56.24,Base,,0,0,0,,It sounds so cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.80,0:21:01.43,Base,,0,0,0,,Hey, if there's something I want to forget, but can't,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.43,0:21:02.59,Base,,0,0,0,,what should I do about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.14,0:21:08.04,Base,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Not surprised. Anybody would be weirded\Nout by a random question like that.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.02,0:21:14.05,Base,,0,0,0,,Well, I'm only 15, so there's a lot\NI have to learn about the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.06,0:21:17.02,Base,,0,0,0,,If you can't forget something that happened,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.02,0:21:21.86,Base,,0,0,0,,you can make new memories by having fun and doing the things you love.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.86,0:21:25.95,Base,,0,0,0,,Just keep overwriting the bad memories \Nwith lots of good ones,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.95,0:21:29.65,Base,,0,0,0,,and eventually, the bad ones will fade away.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.50,0:21:34.71,Base,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Because I was walking behind her,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.71,0:21:37.30,Base,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I couldn't see the expression\Non her face when she said that.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.00,0:21:41.42,Base,,0,0,0,,{\i1}When we got back, the second-years were waiting for us.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.42,0:21:47.75,Base,,0,0,0,,{\i1}For the following week, \NWatanabe and I had our cleaning hours doubled.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.78,0:22:27.64,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur9}Try opening that tightly and strongly clenched fist
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.90,0:22:33.54,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur9}Pieces of dreams will fall off from the palm
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.12,0:22:40.74,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur9}Gently put the important ones on the fingertips
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.20,0:22:44.38,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur9}Butterflies' wings are spreading
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.38,0:22:47.62,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur9}Petals are scattering
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.62,0:22:50.62,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur9}Gracefully than anything
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.88,0:22:58.96,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur9}If you just wanna move forward, forget lovers and friends
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.20,0:23:05.43,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur9}Dreams that lose their radiance become nothing but a stone
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.74,0:23:11.88,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur9}Let's fly higher than anyone
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.20,0:23:17.84,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur9}while tenderly embracing our dreams
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.08,0:23:37.96,Base,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"Act 5: The Chosen Maidens"
